lscan                                 macro                                lscan

NAME
     llssccaann - scan along the LL-axis in reciprocal space

SYNOPSIS

     llssccaann ssttaarrtt eenndd iinntteerrvvaallss ttiimmee

DESCRIPTION

     llssccaann is a linear scan in reciprocal space along the LL-axis from ssttaarrtt to
     eenndd. The step size is (ssttaarrtt--eenndd))//iinntteerrvvaallss.  The number of data points
     collected will be iinntteerrvvaallss++11.  Count time is given by ttiimmee, which if
     positive, specifies seconds and if negative, specifies monitor counts.

EXAMPLE

     llssccaann ..99 11..11 1100 1100

